bugzillatools-0.1.1 :: Tue Jun 14 2011
======================================

New features
------------

- ``products`` command: list products of a Bugzilla.
- Describe subcommands in ``--help`` output.

Bug fixes
---------

- Handle server lookup failure when no servers are defined.


